casebody.data:
Antoine L. CLARK, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 80977 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: December 4, 2018 Laura Martin, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Shaun Mackelprang, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division Two: Alok Ahuja, P.J., Thomas H. Newton, and Mark D. Pfeiffer, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Mr. Antoine L. Clark appeals the Jackson County Circuit Court judgment denying his post-conviction relief motion. For reasons stated in the memorandum provided to the parties, we affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
